    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The class provides methods to handle the boot counter which is stored persitently in flash file system. Boot count is read at startup and is stored in private variable boot_count. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
